:: CC-Name [creation-page nobr]
<h1>Choose your Name</h1>
<br>
What is your name?
<br>
<<textbox "$mc.name" "">>
<br>
<div id="nameError"></div>
<br>
<<button "Confirm">>
	<<if !$mc.name || !$mc.name.trim()>>
		<<replace "#nameError">>
			<span class="red">You must enter a name before continuing.</span>
		<</replace>>
	<<else>>
		<<set $mc.name = $mc.name.trim()>>
		<<goto "Index-CC">>
	<</if>>
<</button>>